{"tid":2441231,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"主場效率太高 有冇人好似我咁未入夠貨","createTime":"2021-03-10T13:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T13:59:04.000Z","uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d149f782a038cfab94ee3f293637c080ad4d9b","tid":2441231,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:52:54.000Z","msg":"其實之前一直跌咁耐 跌到上星期四先到左合理價格 星期五個一陣大跌 係入左折扣時段 所以星期四同五我入左小小貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢 以為兵荒馬亂會有好野執 點知大家都係格價高手 其實市場度仲有好多理性既人 一到左特價就掃野 狼死到不得了<br />\n<br />\n一日已經升到過左價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為會有幾日俾我慢慢揀嘢"},{"pid":"5af982df87a435169f10c8d85867cbcd23f88381","tid":2441231,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"火箭已經升空喇仲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339214a0418706d5fe8814aa87b26da26a409d82","tid":2441231,"uid":36567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:55:52.000Z","msg":"仲等乜呀 上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471b245fcf6c01a3b370d058c602a0f5bed2e162","tid":2441231,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5af982df87a435169f10c8d85867cbcd23f88381","tid":2441231,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"火箭已經升空喇仲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等埋啊"},{"pid":"8422cd79d5fbbb9bd38e097125fc2b57a2d950b1","tid":2441231,"uid":15623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":